    "updated_at": "2017-07-18T21:24:48Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Workaround is to provide an absolute path to to some ancestor directory as an `--allow-paths` parameter and then include a full path to the file as one of the `urls` in `--standard-json`.\r\n\r\n```\r\necho '{\"language\": \"Solidity\", \"sources\": { \"file.sol\": { \"urls\": [ \"/full/path/to/file.sol\" ] } } }' | solc --allow-paths /full/path --standard-json\r\n```",
